<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Connor Snelling</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&family=Caveat:wght@600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #111;
      background: #fff;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 80px 24px 120px;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    a:hover { text-decoration: none; }

    .hero { margin-bottom: 56px; }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: 'Caveat', cursive;
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.1;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .hero p { color: #444; }
    .hero p + p { margin-top: 16px; }

    .hero-links {
      margin-top: 32px;
      display: flex;
      gap: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .hero-links a {
      color: #111;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #111;
      padding-bottom: 1px;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      transition: gap 0.2s ease;
    }

    .hero-links a:hover { gap: 8px; }

    .substack-link {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
      margin-top: 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #111;
      padding-bottom: 1px;
      transition: gap 0.2s ease;
    }

    .substack-link:hover { gap: 8px; }

    hr {
      border: none;
      border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e8;
      margin: 56px 0;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 11px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #999;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    p { color: #444; }

    .brands { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 8px; }

    .brand-tag {
      font-size: 13px;
      padding: 5px 12px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
      color: #555;
      border-radius: 2px;
    }

    .skills-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr);
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .skill-tag {
      font-size: 12px;
      padding: 7px 8px;
      background: #f4f4f4;
      color: #444;
      border-radius: 2px;
      text-align: center;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .stat-val {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .stat-lbl { font-size: 12px; color: #999; }

    footer { margin-top: 80px; font-size: 12px; color: #bbb; }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      .stats {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        gap: 8px;
      }

      .stat-val { font-size: 20px; }
      .stat-lbl { font-size: 11px; }

      .skills-list {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Hi, I'm Connor.</h1>
    <p>I'm in my twenties, living and working in London. I'm currently a manager at WPP, the world's largest marketing organisation, where I specialise in performance marketing.</p>
    <p>I use this site to share thoughts, resources, career updates and anything else worth writing down. Over the past 5+ years I've worked across pretty much every corner of digital marketing. I've led paid media teams managing over £5m+ in spend, managed large websites with millions of visitors and worked with some huge brands like KFC, TK Maxx, eToro etc.</p>
    <div class="hero-links">
      <a href="mailto:connorsnelling@gmail.com">Get in touch →</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/connorsnelling" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn →</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <hr />

  <section>
    <h2>By the numbers</h2>
    <div class="stats">
      <div>
        <div class="stat-val">5+</div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Years experience</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-val">£5m+</div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Ad spend managed</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="stat-val">∞</div>
        <div class="stat-lbl">Hours spent online</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section>
    <h2>Brands I've worked with</h2>
    <div class="brands">
      <span class="brand-tag">eToro</span>
      <span class="brand-tag">Unilever</span>
      <span class="brand-tag">M&amp;S</span>
      <span class="brand-tag">TK Maxx</span>
      <span class="brand-tag">Mazda</span>
      <span class="brand-tag">KFC</span>
      <span class="brand-tag">First Group</span>
      <span class="brand-tag">SWR</span>
      <span class="brand-tag">GWR</span>
      <span class="brand-tag">Avanti</span>
      <span class="brand-tag">Virgin Media</span>
      <span class="brand-tag">Amazon</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section>
    <h2>Substack</h2>
    <p>I write about all things productivity and mindset through achievable, sustainable methods on my Substack, Quiet Progress.</p>
    <a class="substack-link" href="https://open.substack.com/pub/quietprogressuk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Read more on Substack →</a>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section>
    <h2>Core skills</h2>
    <div class="skills-list">
      <span class="skill-tag">Google Ads</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Microsoft Ads</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Meta Ads</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Apple Ads</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">LinkedIn Ads</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Pinterest Ads</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">GA4</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">WordPress</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">AI Tools</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Data Analysis</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">HTML</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">CSS</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">SEO</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">CRO</span>
      <span class="skill-tag">Copywriting</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Whether you're a fellow digital enthusiast, marketer, productivity/tech nerd, or just fancy a chat feel free to reach out.</p>
    <div class="hero-links" style="margin-top:16px">
      <a href="mailto:connorsnelling@gmail.com">Email me →</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/connorsnelling" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LinkedIn →</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>© 2026 Connor Snelling</footer>

</body>
</html>